import React from 'react';
import { Box } from '../components/Box';
import { Flex } from '../components/Flex';
import { Text } from '../components/Text';

function Home() {
  return (
    <Box>
      <Flex
        css={{
          padding: '$5 $6',
          flexWrap: 'wrap',
          gap: '$6',
        }}
      >
        <TextTable weight="regular" />
        <TextTable weight="medium" />
        <TextTable weight="semibold" />
        <TextTable weight="bold" />
      </Flex>

      <Box
        css={{
          padding: '$5 $6',
          display: 'flex',
          flexDirection: 'column',
          gap: '$3',
        }}
      >
        <Text size="5" weight="regular">
          No need to worry 'bout tomorrow, and yesterday is gone
        </Text>
        <Text size="5" weight="medium">
          No need to worry 'bout tomorrow, and yesterday is gone
        </Text>
        <Text size="5" weight="semibold">
          No need to worry 'bout tomorrow, and yesterday is gone
        </Text>
        <Text size="5" weight="bold">
          No need to worry 'bout tomorrow, and yesterday is gone
        </Text>
      </Box>
    </Box>
  );
}

export default Home;

    css={{
      display: 'grid',
      gap: '$3',

      // gridTemplateRows: 'repeat(9, max-content)',

      alignItems: 'baseline',
      textAlign: 'center',
    }}
  >
    <Text weight={weight} size="9">
      Aa
    </Text>
    <Text weight={weight} size="9">
      Bb
    </Text>
    {/* <Text weight={weight} size="9">
      Cc
    </Text> */}

    <Text weight={weight} size="6">

    <Text weight={weight} size="6">

    <Text weight={weight} size="5">
